external_knowledge:
- 'goldmine' refers to the stock portfolio; 
- 'hidden treasure' refers to the unrealized profit or loss from the stock; 
- 'unearthed' refers to the calculation of the unrealized profit or loss.

sql:
SELECT s.stock_name
FROM stocks s
WHERE s.market_cap = (SELECT MAX(market_cap) FROM stocks);

